  "titles": "Lord Commander Eidolon The Auric Hammer, the Exemplar, Lord Commander Primus of the Emperor’s Children",
  "lore": "At one time, Lord Commander Eidolon was hailed as the exemplar of all that the Emperor’s Children aspired to. If Eidolon had any imperfection, it was overconfidence, a characteristic that bore rotten fruit as it was twisted into overweening arrogance. In striving towards the perfection embodied by his Primarch, Eidolon submitted himself to the attentions of Chief Apothecary Fabius, receiving augmentations that allowed him to project a psycho-sonic dirge as formidable as any weapon. The Lord Commander’s skill and his augmented powers were given full rein upon Isstvan V, where he unleashed a cacophonous storm upon the Loyalists.",
